12:49.110 --> 12:50.230
(Jenny chuckles)
Great.

12:52.100 --> 12:55.030
- Hey you call me if
you need anything.

12:57.080 --> 12:59.170
- Um, I don't have your number.

12:59.170 --> 13:01.040
- Oh, here.

13:01.040 --> 13:05.000
